summary: Since one of my favorite Nord and Viking Movies is the 13thWarrior and Skyrim is the land of the nords i dicided to do a Player Home for my Character a Viking Ship dedicated to Tiber Septim; and now i dicided to share it with all skyrim fans .
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a Player Home inspired in the Viking Ship in the 13th Warrior Movie.
This Viking Ship is located near Windhelm docks and its called The Tiber Septim in honor of the Nords to Talos. The ship can be accessed by the skyrim world map. I hope that every one likes it.
Just place the VikingShip.esp file in your skyrim data folder and select it before launching the game.
author: Sergeynest
